description \
                    libqalculate is math libary for expression evaluation \
                    with units, variables and functions support and CAS \
                    functionality.

long_description \
                    libqalculate is math libary for expression evaluation \
                    with units, variables and functions support and CAS \
                    functionality.  This library directly supports the \
                    GUI interface qalculate-gtk or qalculate-kde.

